  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed replacement UPVC windows and doors would appear incongruous and discordant in their visual context and would fail to harmonise with the prevailing pattern of window treatments and materials within the locality. The proposed replacement window are considered to have a detrimental impact on the character and appearance of the building and the surrounding area as a whole. Therefore the proposal is contrary to policy CS9 of the Core Strategy (2011), policy DM 2.1 of the Islington Development Management Policies (2013) and the Islington Urban design Guide (2006)."
